6
00:02:37,173 --> 00:02:41,442
{\an1}We are leaving the rest up to
you now, Kakashi, Sakura...

7
00:02:41,909 --> 00:02:44,444
{\an1}Plus Sasuke and Naruto.

8
00:02:46,746 --> 00:02:47,780
Lord Third!

9
00:02:49,647 --> 00:02:54,649
{\an4}Elder Brother, you've now
finally settled things with
Madara. As Saru just said to
them...

10
00:02:54,683 --> 00:02:57,418
{\an1}...let's leave the rest of it to
the next generation.

11
00:03:06,256 --> 00:03:08,824
{\an1}(HASHIRAMA) <i>Naruto Uzumaki...</i>

12
00:03:08,858 --> 00:03:10,592
<i>Sasuke Uchiha...</i>

13
00:03:12,925 --> 00:03:19,430
{\an7}<i>You two will probably find a</i>
<i>different conclusion that we</i>
<i>did. No... make sure that you do</i>
<i>so.</i>

14
00:03:36,938 --> 00:03:40,641
{\an7}(FOUR TAILS) <i>And now all the</i>
<i>rest of us are free, too!</i>

15
00:03:40,674 --> 00:03:43,777
{\an7}<i>I'm going back to Suirendo!</i>
[chuckle]

16
00:03:44,843 --> 00:03:47,645
{\an7}<i>I believe I'll just hunker down</i>
<i>in a forest.</i>

17
00:03:47,678 --> 00:03:55,115
{\an7}<i>All of us are finally going to</i>
<i>be able to go back to our homes</i>
<i>now. I can't believe it's</i>
<i>true. It's like a dream!</i>

18
00:03:55,149 --> 00:03:58,316
{\an7}<i>Eight Tails, and what will you</i>
<i>do?</i>

19
00:03:58,350 --> 00:04:01,752
{\an7}<i>Who, me? I was thinkiing...</i>

20
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,620
{\an8}<i>Hmmm?</i>

21
00:04:05,354 --> 00:04:08,823
{\an7}<i>I think I'm gonna go back to</i>
<i>being partners with Bee.</i>

22
00:04:08,856 --> 00:04:13,258
{\an7}<i>Even that annoying rapping that</i>
<i>he does has ended up growing on</i>
<i>me.</i>

23
00:04:13,925 --> 00:04:15,592
{\an7}<i>So, what's your plan?</i>

24
00:04:16,026 --> 00:04:17,795
{\an8}<i>Huh? Hmmm...?</i>

25
00:04:17,828 --> 00:04:19,662
{\an7}(EIGHT TAILS) <i>What will you do?</i>

26
00:04:19,695 --> 00:04:20,395
{\an8}<i>Hm.</i>

27
00:04:21,897 --> 00:04:23,564
{\an8}<i>Well... I'll...</i>

28
00:04:27,733 --> 00:04:32,903
{\an7}(HAGOROMO) <i>A little piece of</i>
<i>each of your chakra... is</i>
<i>already inside of Naruto.</i>

29
00:04:34,135 --> 00:04:38,238
{\an1}In short, Naruto is like a
gathering place for you Tailed
Beasts.

30
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:45,642
{\an4}If you want to discuss
something, you can speak to each
other through your chakra within
Naruto. Kurama...

31
00:04:45,675 --> 00:04:46,409
{\an9}<i>Huh?</i>

32
00:04:47,877 --> 00:04:51,746
{\an1}I'd like you to stay inside
Naruto as the overseerof the
gathering place.

33
00:04:52,012 --> 00:04:52,879
{\an8}<i>Wha-?!</i>

34
00:04:53,145 --> 00:04:55,581
{\an1}You no longer mind, right?

35
00:04:56,414 --> 00:05:00,483
{\an7}<i>Well... I guess I'll do it if</i>
<i>you insist, old man...</i>

36
00:05:00,516 --> 00:05:03,218
{\an8}[laughter]

37
00:05:03,251 --> 00:05:05,952
{\an7}<i>What is it?! What the heck is so</i>
<i>funny?</i>

38
00:05:05,985 --> 00:05:10,456
{\an7}<i>You still can't be honest </i>
<i>about your feelings! You haven't</i>
<i>changed, Kurama.</i>

39
00:05:10,489 --> 00:05:11,722
[chuckling]

40
00:05:13,223 --> 00:05:17,325
{\an1}It's finally finished. The
Fourth Great Ninja War is over!

41
00:05:17,358 --> 00:05:20,060
{\an1}Yeah. All that's left is...

42
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:25,062
{\an1}Alright, Naruto and Sasuke...
About what I asked you two
before...

43
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:31,233
{\an1}Having battled my mother
Kaguya... is there any change to
the answers you gave me?

44
00:05:34,902 --> 00:05:39,404
{\an1}My answer's the same. And I'm
sorry, Super Gramps, but after
fighting Kaguya...

45
00:05:39,871 --> 00:05:43,072
{\an1}...there's just one thing I feel
strongly about...

46
00:05:43,739 --> 00:05:48,709
{\an1}I'm just really happy that my
mom was Kushina Uzumaki, y'know!

47
00:05:49,409 --> 00:05:52,744
{\an1}<i>Kaguya was different from anyone</i>
<i>else I've ever fought against...</i>

48
00:05:53,177 --> 00:05:56,213
{\an1}It's like she didn't even have a
heart at all...

49
00:05:56,480 --> 00:06:02,382
{\an1}Long ago, it was said that my
mother Kaguya started off as a
beloved goddess of the people.

50
00:06:02,683 --> 00:06:07,219
{\an1}I'm not certain what made her
transform into a being that was
called a demon.

51
00:06:08,052 --> 00:06:14,223
{\an1}<i>I suspect that the process, or</i>
<i>something, started after she</i>
<i>devoured the Chakra Fruit.</i>

52
00:06:15,056 --> 00:06:21,392
{\an1}In any case, you are not like my
mother. I trust you not to
become like her, even if...

53
00:06:21,626 --> 00:06:24,561
{\an1}...you have all the Tailed
Beasts' Chakra in you.

54
00:06:25,395 --> 00:06:30,397
{\an1}Now then, all that's left... is
to undo the Infinate Tsukuyomi.

55
00:06:30,898 --> 00:06:35,567
{\an7}<i>But how, specifically? Are you</i>
<i>going to need our powers, as</i>
<i>well?</i>

56
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:41,670
{\an1}No, all of you are just fine.
Naruto possesses the chakra of
every Tailed Beast.

57
00:06:41,704 --> 00:06:48,875
{\an4}<i>And Sasuke posseses the</i>
<i>Rinnegan. If they both weave the</i>
<i>sign for rat simultaneously, the</i>
<i>jutsu will be undone.</i>

58
00:06:49,074 --> 00:06:52,409
{\an7}<i>What? That's it? It'll really be</i>
<i>that easy?</i>

59
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:57,379
{\an1}Believe me, I researched
thoroughly how to undo Mother's
Infinite Tsukuyomi.

60
00:06:58,246 --> 00:06:59,714
{\an1}There's no mistake.

61
00:07:00,247 --> 00:07:04,415
{\an1}Very well, then. Now, Sasuke,
the rest... is up to you.

62
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:12,888
Yeah, alright...

63
00:07:14,555 --> 00:07:18,557
{\an1}But before that, I'm executing
the current Five Kage inside the
Infinate Tsukuyomi.

64
00:07:19,457 --> 00:07:20,258
{\an8}[gasps]

65
00:07:31,697 --> 00:07:33,532
{\an1}What did you just say, Sasuke?!

66
00:07:34,164 --> 00:07:34,865
{\an1}Huh?

67
00:07:35,866 --> 00:07:37,534
{\an1}What about the Five Kage?

68
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:40,368
{\an1}And you Tailed Beasts...

69
00:07:40,802 --> 00:07:46,137
{\an1}I'm putting all of you under my
control, and eventually, I'll
get rid of you as well.

70
00:07:46,170 --> 00:07:47,705
{\an1}What did you just say?

71
00:07:49,339 --> 00:07:50,374
[roar]

72
00:07:50,574 --> 00:07:51,374
Huh?!

73
00:08:00,445 --> 00:08:01,914
{\an8}[struggling]

74
00:08:01,947 --> 00:08:02,914
Kurama!

75
00:08:03,447 --> 00:08:06,048
{\an1}He put the Tailed Beats under a
genjutsu...

76
00:08:06,448 --> 00:08:08,884
{\an1}And with just a single glance,
too...

77
00:08:09,384 --> 00:08:16,220
{\an1}Naruto, it's ended up as I
feared. I've no choice but to
trust you to handle this.

78
00:08:16,488 --> 00:08:20,924
{\an1}I can't stay in this world any
longer. I shall soon fade away.

79
00:08:20,957 --> 00:08:28,028
{\an4}Yeah. And I'll apologize for
this too, Six Paths Super
Gramps, but it ain't gonna go
like it did with your kids.

80
00:08:28,994 --> 00:08:31,194
{\an1}That's because I'm not Ashura.

81
00:08:31,696 --> 00:08:34,196
{\an1}<i>And Sasuke... isn't Indra</i>
<i>either.</i>

82
00:08:34,864 --> 00:08:40,868
{\an4}(KAKASHI) <i>Sasuke! Is this what</i>
<i>your current dream is? Are you</i>
<i>saying that you're still seeking</i>
<i>vengeance?</i>

83
00:08:42,001 --> 00:08:43,368
{\an1}Why, Sasuke?!

84
00:08:43,635 --> 00:08:44,703
{\an1}I admit...

85
00:08:46,169 --> 00:08:49,204
{\an1}...at one time, all that I
wanted was to seek vengeance and
destruction.

86
00:08:49,505 --> 00:08:51,539
{\an1}But now, things are different.

87
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:55,708
{\an1}I want to destroy but then I
want to rebuild.

88
00:08:56,208 --> 00:09:00,544
{\an1}A village without darkness. I'll
reform the shinobi world.

89
00:09:00,711 --> 00:09:03,446
[straining]

90
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:07,014
{\an1}(SASUKE) <i>Do you understand? What</i>
<i>I'm talking about...</i>

91
00:09:08,782 --> 00:09:10,349
{\an1}...is revolution!

92
00:09:11,017 --> 00:09:12,851
{\an1}Revolution, you say?!

93
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,020
My dear Sasuke...

94
00:09:18,621 --> 00:09:23,057
{\an1}What do you want to do? What is
it that you seek for the
aftermath of this war?

95
00:09:23,289 --> 00:09:26,358
{\an1}I would like to hear your
honest thoughts and opinions.

96
00:09:29,259 --> 00:09:32,528
{\an1}The previous Kage caused these
circumstances.

97
00:09:33,028 --> 00:09:35,029
{\an1}So I will become Hokage...

98
00:09:35,262 --> 00:09:36,530
{\an1}...and change the Village.

99
00:09:39,532 --> 00:09:44,100
{\an1}This title of "Hokage" that you
mentioned... Just what do you
mean by it?

100
00:09:44,133 --> 00:09:47,102
{\an1}If you want to know so badly,
I'll tell you.

101
00:09:49,604 --> 00:09:52,005
{\an1}Catastrophic Planetary
Devistation!

102
00:10:06,112 --> 00:10:09,081
[gasps]

103
00:10:09,113 --> 00:10:10,348
[growl]

104
00:10:13,883 --> 00:10:16,852
{\an1}It's up to you, Naruto!

105
00:10:17,885 --> 00:10:20,854
{\an1}I swear I'll rescue you all!
I'll save you!

106
00:10:26,624 --> 00:10:29,358
{\an1}Just hang in there a little
while longer, okay?!

107
00:10:39,162 --> 00:10:40,497
{\an1}Because of this war...

108
00:10:41,965 --> 00:10:44,332
{\an1}...I've already become quite
adept at using my Rinnenegan's
abilities.

109
00:10:45,001 --> 00:10:48,334
{\an1}<i>And all those who were in my way</i>
<i>are gone.</i>

110
00:10:52,336 --> 00:10:54,338
{\an1}Except for you... Naruto.

111
00:10:57,406 --> 00:10:59,674
{\an1}Things just don't go as planned.

112
00:10:59,907 --> 00:11:05,343
{\an1}When I decided to bequeath power
to just one side, I ended up
with Indra and Ashura.

113
00:11:05,678 --> 00:11:10,680
{\an1}<i>This time, I bequeathed it to</i>
<i>both, yet it still ended up the</i>
<i>same way...</i>

114
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:11,848
[exhale]

115
00:11:16,483 --> 00:11:21,185
{\an1}No way... All this stupid
squabbling... is gonna end right
here and now!

116
00:11:35,861 --> 00:11:40,996
{\an1}First off, let the Tailed Beasts
go. I mean, they just finally
got their freedom back!

117
00:12:01,774 --> 00:12:07,576
{\an4}I'm friends with all of them, so
I can guaruntee you this... They
aren't gonna cause trouble any
longer.

118
00:12:07,811 --> 00:12:11,146
{\an1}Naruto... you don't seem to
understand at all.

119
00:12:12,946 --> 00:12:16,815
{\an1}As it stands, you're now the
Jinchuriki of all the Tailed
Beasts.

120
00:12:16,848 --> 00:12:22,886
{\an4}And what that means is that I
plan to eventually get rid of
the Tailed Beast Chakra in you
too.

121
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:23,318
{\an3}[gasp]

122
00:12:23,686 --> 00:12:24,820
{\an1}What?! No way...

123
00:12:26,319 --> 00:12:30,823
{\an1}In short, you're going to die,
Naruto. Out of necessity.

124
00:12:34,258 --> 00:12:36,459
{\an1}If what the Sage said is
true...

125
00:12:36,492 --> 00:12:41,996
{\an4}the Tailed Beast power
inside you isn't necessary in
order for me to release
the Infinite Tsukuyomi.

126
00:12:42,996 --> 00:12:48,231
{\an1}<i>I can just use the Tailed Beasts</i>
<i>themselves that I captured. I'll</i>
<i>let them live until then.</i>

127
00:12:48,265 --> 00:12:52,333
{\an1}I'm not gonna stand here and let
you hurt the,. You know that,
don't you?

128
00:12:57,804 --> 00:13:01,305
{\an1}As expected, I'll have to deal
with you first, Naruto.

129
00:13:04,474 --> 00:13:08,309
{\an1}Let's move this elsewhere. you
understand, of course?

130
00:13:12,978 --> 00:13:13,979
Wait, Sasuke!

131
00:13:14,312 --> 00:13:15,212
[pained grunt]

132
00:13:15,245 --> 00:13:16,147
{\an1}Sensei!

133
00:13:16,547 --> 00:13:18,548
{\an1}[heavy breathing]

134
00:13:18,581 --> 00:13:20,982
{\an1}The Sharingan's aftereffect is
still...!

135
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,861
[quivering]

136
00:13:41,894 --> 00:13:47,296
{\an1}I... I know in my heart that
there's nothing I can do, even
though I love you!

137
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:50,631
{\an1}<i>Even though I care so much about</i>
<i>you, Sasuke!</i>

138
00:13:51,466 --> 00:13:53,967
{\an1}<i>I can't get close to you or</i>
<i>exchange blows with you.</i>

139
00:13:55,301 --> 00:13:58,770
{\an1}I can only whine, beg, and cry,
yet again.

140
00:13:58,803 --> 00:14:01,304
{\an1}It's so pitiful, isn't it?

141
00:14:05,173 --> 00:14:06,140
Sakura...

142
00:14:08,408 --> 00:14:09,341
I thank you.

143
00:14:11,642 --> 00:14:14,377
{\an1}But... but please, Sasuke!

144
00:14:14,411 --> 00:14:19,814
{\an4}If there's even a little corner
of your heart that still thinks
about me, don't leave again!
Please!

145
00:14:20,647 --> 00:14:27,485
{\an1}<i>If we just stick together... I</i>
<i>know that it can be like old</i>
<i>times again... someday...</i>

146
00:14:29,519 --> 00:14:30,787
You really are...

147
00:14:31,887 --> 00:14:33,788
{\an1}...still incredibly annoying.

148
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,126
[gasp]

149
00:14:52,132 --> 00:14:52,965
Sakura!

150
00:14:53,966 --> 00:14:55,967
{\an1}You didn't need to put Sakura
under genjutsu!

151
00:14:56,466 --> 00:14:57,467
{\an1}If I didn't...

152
00:14:58,734 --> 00:15:01,469
{\an1}...then she would've just chased
after us and gotten in the way.

153
00:15:02,137 --> 00:15:06,806
{\an1}Sakura... Sakura just wanted to
help you. All this time...

154
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:09,473
{\an1}You're suggesting that I enjoy a
romance?

155
00:15:09,507 --> 00:15:13,977
{\an1}Too bad I have no reason to love
her or to be loved by her.

156
00:15:14,676 --> 00:15:20,780
{\an4}The only time that you need a
reason like that is when you
want to <i>hate</i> someone! Don't you
understand?

157
00:15:20,813 --> 00:15:23,348
{\an1}Sakura isn't even trying to make
you hers!

158
00:15:23,381 --> 00:15:32,519
{\an4}She only wants to save you! She
almost died by your hand, but
even now... She still spills
tears for you!

159
00:15:32,552 --> 00:15:34,954
{\an1}<i>She suffers from loving you!</i>

160
00:15:37,822 --> 00:15:39,157
Uh, hey Mom...

161
00:15:39,589 --> 00:15:40,290
Hm?

162
00:15:42,024 --> 00:15:46,293
{\an1}I was wondering... It's about my
brother and me... What does
father really think of us?

163
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:49,461
{\an1}Hm? What on earth makes you ask
that?

164
00:15:50,495 --> 00:15:54,731
{\an1}The other day, down on the dock,
father said to me, "That's my
boy."

165
00:15:55,465 --> 00:16:01,002
{\an1}That's something he's only ever
said to Itachi. So it made me
really happy to hear it.

166
00:16:01,035 --> 00:16:01,902
[chuckle]

167
00:16:01,935 --> 00:16:04,435
{\an1}I see... that's great to hear.

168
00:16:04,770 --> 00:16:09,772
{\an1}But then I started to wonder,
now that Father and Itachi
aren't getting along...

169
00:16:12,275 --> 00:16:13,340
Am I just...

170
00:16:13,374 --> 00:16:15,775
{\an1}...someone to replace my older
brother?

171
00:16:18,944 --> 00:16:19,778
[sigh]

172
00:16:22,512 --> 00:16:25,281
{\an1}Your older brother's your older
brother, and you're you.

173
00:16:25,548 --> 00:16:29,783
{\an1}Believe me, your father has
always cared very deeply about
the both of you.

174
00:16:30,150 --> 00:16:32,350
{\an1}He's only thought of Itachi
before now!

175
00:16:32,384 --> 00:16:33,852
{\an1}<i>If it seemed that</i>
<i>way...</i>

176
00:16:35,653 --> 00:16:38,788
{\an1}...the reason for that's simple.
It's because your father is a
leader of the Uchiha Clan...

177
00:16:38,822 --> 00:16:41,256
{\an1}and he has to make sure that
it's kept safe and secure.

178
00:16:41,290 --> 00:16:42,723
{\an1}What's that got to do with it?

179
00:16:42,757 --> 00:16:46,026
{\an1}Your brother is the first born.
He's older than you are.

180
00:16:50,261 --> 00:16:53,663
{\an1}<i>So, since it's your father's job</i>
<i>to look after the clan...</i>

181
00:16:53,696 --> 00:16:58,531
{\an1}<i>it's only natural he'd want to</i>
<i>be sure that Itachi's ready to</i>
<i>take on his role.</i>

182
00:16:58,565 --> 00:17:00,999
{\an1}But I'll let you in on a secret.

183
00:17:01,033 --> 00:17:06,102
{\an1}When we're alone and no one's
around, the only one that he
talks about is... you, Sasuke!

184
00:17:07,369 --> 00:17:12,272
{\an1}He's so serious, and he has a
hard time showing his feelings;
it's how he is.

185
00:17:24,812 --> 00:17:26,113
{\an1}Got your lunch ready.

186
00:17:26,147 --> 00:17:27,113
Time to go.

187
00:17:28,781 --> 00:17:31,616
{\an1}And after you get home today,
I'll watch you practice your
shuriken jutsu. Okay?

188
00:17:31,916 --> 00:17:34,550
{\an1}It's not "practice." It's called
training.

189
00:17:34,584 --> 00:17:35,585
See you later!

190
00:17:35,918 --> 00:17:37,153
Have a great day!

