00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:44,456
{\an1}Well, perhaps, those are merely
the ties to a failed past.

192
00:17:47,924 --> 00:17:48,758
{\an8}<i>Sasuke...!</i>

193
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:51,593
{\an7}(NARUTO) <i>I made a promise...</i>

194
00:17:52,927 --> 00:17:55,461
{\an1}To Sakura a long time ago...

195
00:17:56,196 --> 00:17:59,264
{\an1}Don't you worry one bit. I'm
gonna bring Sasuke back.

196
00:17:59,931 --> 00:18:01,932
{\an1}I promise that on my life
Sakura!

197
00:18:02,866 --> 00:18:06,268
{\an1}Well, Sensei... You already know
my Ninja Way, right?

198
00:18:06,734 --> 00:18:07,768
I'm gonna go!

199
00:18:10,170 --> 00:18:13,105
{\an1}Alright... We're counting on
you.

200
00:18:23,409 --> 00:18:25,745
{\an1}(HAGOROMO) <i>Love and affection</i>
<i>are difficult things...</i>

201
00:18:26,778 --> 00:18:29,412
{\an1}I too, had two children at one
time.

202
00:18:30,014 --> 00:18:33,649
{\an1}I loved both of them, and they
both loved and revered me.

203
00:18:34,415 --> 00:18:37,918
{\an1}<i>But I entrusted everything </i>
<i>only to the younger brother.</i>

204
00:18:38,417 --> 00:18:46,422
{\an4}<i>That became the impetus for the</i>
<i>older brother to begin hating me</i>
<i>and his brother. Love had</i>
<i>transformed into hate.</i>

205
00:18:47,589 --> 00:18:52,926
{\an1}<i>What molded the current</i>
<i>Sasuke... is none other than his</i>
<i>loss of love in the past.</i>

206
00:18:54,526 --> 00:18:55,760
{\an1}<i>Madara was the same.</i>

207
00:18:57,762 --> 00:19:03,098
{\an1}Are you saying that Sasuke... is
going to suffer the same fate as
Madara?

208
00:19:03,298 --> 00:19:04,932
{\an1}No, I'm not at all.

209
00:19:05,132 --> 00:19:09,434
{\an1}I also want to make the future a
better place, in my own way.

210
00:19:09,701 --> 00:19:12,236
{\an1}Having learned from my past
mistakes...

211
00:19:12,970 --> 00:19:16,238
{\an1}This time I gave both of them
the power instead.

212
00:19:17,072 --> 00:19:21,141
{\an1}The past insn't there to
remind the present that the
future can't change.

213
00:19:21,174 --> 00:19:24,176
{\an1}The past is supposed to exist
for the future.

214
00:19:24,210 --> 00:19:27,410
{\an1}Why exactly do you see potential
within Naruto?

215
00:19:32,347 --> 00:19:38,416
{\an4}Somehow, that boy was able to
save and befriend Kurama, who
had become a concretion of
hatred.

216
00:19:39,084 --> 00:19:41,585
{\an1}I think I shall let Naruto
handle this...

217
00:19:42,252 --> 00:19:46,254
{\an1}<i>...since I hope that hate can be</i>
<i>transformed into love this</i>
<i>time...</i>

218
00:19:47,255 --> 00:19:51,590
{\an1}<i>Or rather... I have hope that</i>
<i>love can be regained.</i>

219
00:19:55,558 --> 00:20:03,063
{\an1}<i>Since, unlike my mother...</i>
<i>Naruto, as well as Sauke...</i>
<i>knows what love truely is.</i>

220
00:20:04,064 --> 00:20:09,066
{\an1}This place, huh? Should've
figured. Brings back memories,
right, Sasuke?

221
00:20:09,466 --> 00:20:13,735
{\an1}This place was where we battled
against each other. Seems so
long ago...

222
00:20:14,202 --> 00:20:18,805
{\an1}It'll be the same now. Just like
the last time... you're going to
lose here.

223
00:20:18,838 --> 00:20:23,674
{\an1}But you aren't gonna be able to
hit me with the same punch as
last time!

224
00:20:23,707 --> 00:20:26,742
{\an1}<i>There's no way I'm gonna let you</i>
<i>get away with whatever you want.</i>

225
00:20:28,077 --> 00:20:31,812
{\an1}And trust me, Sasuke you're not
gonna be Hokage, either!

226
00:20:31,845 --> 00:20:35,414
{\an1}You don't even seem to
understand what it means to be
Hokage.

227
00:20:35,981 --> 00:20:40,582
{\an1}I told you, being Hokage means
revolution to me.

228
00:20:40,816 --> 00:20:43,052
{\an1}It's totally different than what
you believe.

229
00:20:43,451 --> 00:20:46,887
{\an1}Your big brother once said
something to me. Lemme tell
ya...

230
00:20:47,321 --> 00:20:51,389
{\an1}Becoming Hokage isn't all about
getting people to acknowledge
you.

231
00:20:51,722 --> 00:20:55,391
{\an1}<i>Only those already acknowledged</i>
<i>will ever become Hokage.</i>

232
00:20:55,824 --> 00:21:00,894
{\an1}Well, I learned not from
Itachi's words, but by the way
that he lived his life.

233
00:21:02,195 --> 00:21:08,231
{\an1}You and I simply arrived at
different conclusions. Let me
clarify this before we fight...

234
00:21:09,399 --> 00:21:13,867
{\an1}I'll teach you exactly what
being Hokage means to me now.

235
00:21:13,901 --> 00:21:14,734
[scoff]

236
00:22:56,922 --> 00:23:00,891
{\an1}(NARUTO) <i>You really don't have</i>
<i>any clue at all about how Itachi</i>
<i>lived!</i>

237
00:23:00,924 --> 00:23:07,527
{\an4}(SASUKE) <i>As of now, Itachi is</i>
<i>entirely in the past. I'm</i>
<i>cutting ties with past mistakes</i>
<i>and doubts.</i>

238
00:23:08,528 --> 00:23:15,766
{\an4}<i>I'm going to begin by cutting</i>
<i>you down. Yours will be the last</i>
<i>blood that I shed in the memory</i>
<i>of my late brother.</i>

239
00:23:16,532 --> 00:23:20,201
{\an1}(NARUTO) <i>Next time of Naruro</i>
<i>Shippuden: "The Final Battle."</i>

240
00:23:21,202 --> 00:23:22,568
<i>I won't let you!</i>

